name: ROBQR S1-03
description:
| Collection: ROBQR VQGAN+CLIP Minibot Series.

| Type: Limited edition, generative AI illustrations.

| Characters: Textual ninety-character compositions processed with VQGAN and CLIP.

| Compositions: eg. Dawn of Singularity, cataclysmic shift in the Anthropocene.

| Excerpts: Concepts, topics, themes in https://ro.uow.edu.au/theses1/853/. 

| Scale: 1200 x 1200px, 144 DPI.

| Format: PNG-24, 16-bit sRGB, iEC61966-2.1 format.

| Interpolation: 2xSaI, 4X upscale xBRZ, Affinity Photo.

| Color Grading: EnhanceAI, StructureAI and RelightAI, LuminarNeo.
